{"title":"用conda创建python虚拟环境","date":"2018-10-20T16:00:00.000Z","slug":"用conda创建python虚拟环境","comments":true,"tags":["命令"],"updated":"2018-10-21T16:00:00.000Z","content":"<ol>\n<li>conda常用的命令</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight zsh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conda -V <span class=\"comment\"># 查看版本</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">conda list <span class=\"comment\"># 查看安装了哪些包。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">conda env list 或 conda info -e <span class=\"comment\"># 查看当前存在哪些虚拟环境</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">conda update conda <span class=\"comment\"># 检查更新当前conda</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>创建python虚拟环境。</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight zsh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 命令创建python版本为X.X、名字为your_env_name的虚拟环境。your_env_name文件可以在Anaconda安装目录envs文件下找到。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">conda create -n your_env_name python=X.X（2.7、3.6等)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>使用激活(或切换不同python版本)的虚拟环境。</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight zsh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#打开命令行输入python --version可以检查当前python的版本。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#使用如下命令即可 激活你的虚拟环境(即将python的版本改变)。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Linux:  </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">source</span> activate your_env_name(虚拟环境名称)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Windows: </span></span><br><span class=\"line\">activate your_env_name(虚拟环境名称)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>   这是再使用python –version可以检查当前python版本是否为想要的。</p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>对虚拟环境中安装额外的包。</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># package到your_env_name中</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">conda install -n your_env_name [package]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>关闭虚拟环境(即从当前环境退出返回使用PATH环境中的默认python版本)。</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight zsh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Linux: </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">source</span> deactivate</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Windows: </span></span><br><span class=\"line\">deactivate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li>删除虚拟环境</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight zsh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conda remove -n your_env_name(虚拟环境名称) --all</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"7\">\n<li>删除环境中的某个包</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight zsh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conda remove --name your_env_name  package_name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","next":{"title":"Hello World","slug":"hello-world"},"link":"http://yoursite.com/post/用conda创建python虚拟环境/"}